<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>大模型每日早报 · 历史归档</title>
<style>
  :root { --primary:#5b5bd6; --text:#1d2433; --soft:#657086; --border:#e5e7ef; --bg:#f5f6fa; }
  * { box-sizing:border-box; }
  body { margin:0; font-family:-apple-system,"PingFang SC","Microsoft YaHei","Segoe UI",sans-serif; background:var(--bg); color:var(--text); }
  main { width:min(760px,calc(100% - 34px)); margin:42px auto 72px; }
  .hero { padding:34px 36px; color:#fff; border-radius:24px; background:linear-gradient(125deg,#4c50c8,#8c56df); box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(83,73,190,.2); }
  .eyebrow { font-size:11px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; opacity:.72; text-transform:uppercase; }
  h1 { margin:9px 0 8px; font-size:30px; }
  .hero p { margin:0; opacity:.82; font-size:14px; }
  .back { display:inline-block; margin:22px 0 14px; color:var(--primary); text-decoration:none; font-weight:650; }
  .reports { display:grid; gap:10px; }
  .report { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:17px 19px; color:var(--text); text-decoration:none; background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:14px; box-shadow:0 7px 24px rgba(37,43,67,.045); }
  .report:hover { border-color:#c8c5ef; transform:translateY(-1px); }
  .arrow { color:var(--soft); }
  .empty { padding:24px; color:var(--soft); background:#fff; border:1px dashed var(--border); border-radius:14px; }
  footer { margin-top:22px; color:var(--soft); text-align:center; font-size:12px; }
  @media(max-width:560px) { main { margin-top:0; width:100%; } .hero { border-radius:0 0 22px 22px; padding:32px 22px; } .content { padding:0 17px; } h1 { font-size:26px; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">AI Intelligence Briefing</div>
    <h1>🗂️ 历史早报</h1>
    <p>滚动保留最近 {{ retention_days }} 天，最新内容仍在固定主页。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <a class="back" href="index.html">← 返回最新早报</a>
    <div class="reports">
      {% for report_date in report_dates %}
      <a class="report" href="{{ report_date }}.html"><span>{{ report_date }}</span><span class="arrow">查看 →</span></a>
      {% else %}
      <div class="empty">暂无历史日报。</div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <footer>归档更新于 {{ generated_at }}</footer>
  </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
